      "comment": "PAW ZENITH (1) is having his first start around this course. Comes here a winner at Warrnambool last time in a Grade 5 (25.82). Well placed and can measure up. TURN UP TURBO (8) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.71 beating Skate In Paris. The form from his last run stacks up well. Should be in this for a long way. FOXY BARBELLA (5) turned in a moderate effort last time when sixth at The Meadows over 525m behind Flat Out Freddy (30.63) in a Grade 4/5. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Should be about the money. BILLY RAY MIKADO (2) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
